Great for college goers this Vital Gear Yo Gear 7 Sling Bag – Unisex is a simple yet versatile satchel that would certainly offer long lasting performance while use. This satchel is made of 600 D polyester material thereby ensuring secure and firm support to all the essentials you require carrying along for the day. Designed with compact yet roomy interiors this sling bag comes with the capacity to hold pretty much everything you stash while use. These interiors comprise of four compartments hence allowing you to place your must-haves in order of priority. In addition to this the Vital Gear Yo Gear 7 Sling Bag – Unisex is equipped with a zippered closure that safely encases your things within.

The adjustable shoulder strap in this sling bag undoubtedly offers comfortable and hassle-free portability. Besides this the padded body material padded laptop compartment with elastic band and velcro closure add to the comfort and convenience while use. This bag also comes with padded flap with plastic buckles. Furthermore the nylon zipper compartments with slider allows for easy usage. Measuring 390 x 110 x 300 mm in dimension this Vital Gear Yo Gear 7 Sling Bag – Unisex is lightweight and hence is effortless to carry along on the move.
